3D City Database Importer/Exporter Plugin API - 1.6-postgis

This document is the API specification for the 3D City Database Importer/Exporter Plugin API 1.6-postgis.
The 3D City Database Importer/Exporter Plugin API is a Java class library and API facilitating the development of own extensions for the 3D City Database Importer/Exporter program.
The 3D City Database Importer/Exporter Plugin API is open source and released under the terms of the GNU Lesser General Public License v3 (LGPL).
Official website and more information at: http://www.3dcitydb.net/
Copyright © 2007 - 2013
Institute for Geodesy and Geoinformation Science (IGG)
Technische Universität Berlin, Germany
http://www.igg.tu-berlin.de/
